# Flocq.Core.Spec.Defs

Specifications for the Flocq foundation types. This module is intentionally
empty: `Core.Defs` defines only the `FloatNum` and `RoundingMode` types,
with no computable API functions, and therefore has no function-level specs.
These types serve as the shared vocabulary for all other Flocq modules.

DO NOT MODIFY — this file is frozen curator-given content.
